Really, Really RUDE hostesses today. Walked in about 4:00PM before they got busy. We were told they were setting up a table for 5 of us. A couple minutes later we were told our wait would be 20 minutes. Fine - we'll wait. Another couple minutes later two groups of equal size that walked in behind us were seated and we were informed that "all big tables have been seated and our wait would now be an hour". I pointed right at an empty booth for 6 and asked about that one. They said they're getting ready to seat it. These girls were snotty and condescending. We usually like this place. Never had this kind of problem before. We left and went across the street to try ZinBurger. Thanks Oregano's for turning us on to an amazing burger and salad place.

