Amazing service from the greeting at the door to the friendly and efficient wait staff. Burgers and Double Truffle Fry were fantastic. I got the Asian Chicken Salad. It was fresh, light and full of flavor with crisp vegetables and plenty of grilled chicken. It's a touch pricy but the servings are large and shareable if desired.  We'll be back.

